---
title: Simple Scrambled Eggs
author: Home Cook
servings: 1
prep_time: 2 minutes
cook_time: 3 minutes
tags: breakfast
difficulty: Easy
---

Heat @butter{1%tablespoon} in a #non-stick pan{} over medium-low heat.

Crack @eggs{2%large} into a bowl and whisk with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

Pour eggs into the pan and cook for ~{2-3%minutes}, stirring gently.

Serve immediately.
